Type: Package
Package: gpssampling
Title: GPS Sampling
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yves", "Amevoin", email = "epicentre-msf@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Claude", "(Anthropic AI)", role = "aut")
  )
Description: A Shiny application for geospatial sampling of building
    structures within defined polygon areas. Supports quadrat, T-square,
    and random sampling methods with OpenStreetMap and Google satellite
    imagery integration for field epidemiology surveys. Fork of the
    original GeoSampler package by Epicentre (MSF), modified with Claude
    AI agent assistance for internal use.
License: file LICENSE
URL: https://epicentre-msf.github.io/gpssampling/,
    https://github.com/epicentre-msf/gpssampling
